Interface Menu

All Known Implementing Classes:
CampComMenu, LoginMenu, MainMenu, StaffCampMenu, StaffMenu, StudentCampMenu, StudentMenu
public interface Menu
The Menu interface represents the generic menu that defines printMenu() and viewApp() functions
